column2: SELECT count(*) as &&&,   sum( case when (s.z between # and #) then # else # end) as &&&,  sum( case when (s.z between # and #) then # else # end) as &&&,  sum( case when (s.z between # and #) then # else # end) as &&&,  sum( case when (s.z between # and #) then # else # end) as &&&,  sum( case when (s.z between # and #) then # else # end) as &&&,  sum( case when (s.z between # and #) then # else # end) as &&&,  sum( case when (s.z between # and #) then # else # end) as &&&,  sum( case when (s.z between # and #) then # else # end) as &&&,  sum( case when (s.z between # and #) then # else # end) as &&&,  sum( case when (s.z between # and #) then # else # end) as &&&,  sum( case when (s.z between # and #) then # else # end) as &&&,  sum( case when (s.z between # and #) then # else # end) as &&&,  sum( case when (s.z between # and #) then # else # end) as &&&,  sum( case when (s.z between # and #) then # else # end) as &&&,  sum( case when (s.z between # and #) then # else # end) as &&&,  sum( case when (s.z > #) then # else # end) as &&& FROM WISE_xmatch as xm   JOIN PhotoObj AS p on xm.sdss_objid = p.objid  JOIN SpecObj AS s on p.objid = s.bestobjid  JOIN WISE_allsky AS w on xm.wise_cntr = w.cntr WHERE  s.class=&&& and s.subclass not like &&&
